                        <h3 class="feature-title">Interactive Maps</h3>
                        <p class="feature-description">Discover campgrounds with our advanced map integration and
                            location services</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3">
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <div class="feature-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="feature-title">Verified Reviews</h3>
                        <p class="feature-description">Read authentic reviews from real campers to make informed
